attributes.Long form description: The student disassembles a table. Begins by unscrewing the hex socket heads from the first leg and then the hex socket heads from the second leg and placing the hex socket heads on the table, then the student unscrews the top hex socket heads from the third leg and then the bottom hex socket head from the first leg, the student unscrews the top hex socket head from the fourth leg and then removes the rest of the hex socket heads from the third leg when the student finish removes the top table from the furniture and then removes the last hex socket heads from the fourth leg and then the student disassemble the shelf from the furniture and disassemble the legs off to finally place all on the table.
